Info Terbaru

Ini Script Works All Site (Mobile, Desktop)
Script Terbaru ada Di Bawah 

<!-- Waifu Chara | Paste Di atas </Body>-->
<script src='https://l2dwidget.js.org/lib/L2Dwidget.min.js'/>
    <script type='text/javascript'>

      L2Dwidget
        .init({
           model: {
               jsonPath: &quot;https://unpkg.com/live2d-widget-model-shizuku@1.0.5/assets/shizuku.model.json&quot;},
            display: {
                &quot;position&quot;: &quot;right&quot;,
                &quot;width&quot;: 150,
                &quot;height&quot;: 300,
                &quot;hOffset&quot;: 50,
                &quot;vOffset&quot;: -50,
            },
           mobile: { 
               show: true,
               scale: 1
           },
          dialog: {
            enable: true,
            script: {
              &#39;every idle 10s&#39;: &#39;$hitokoto$&#39;,
              &#39;hover .star&#39;: &#39;kalau bintang-bintang ada di langit, kalau kamu ada di hatiku (*/Ï‰&#65340;*)&#39;,
              &#39;tap body&#39;: &#39;Ups! Jangan sentuh aku!&#39;,
              &#39;tap face&#39;: &#39;Aku bukan anak-anak lagi!&#39;
            }
          }
        });
    </script>  

Bagian json path bisa di ganti sesuai character yang di inginkan

source https://www.yukinoshita.web.id/2020/11/cara-membuat-widget-anime-di-blog.html, https://www.yukinoshita.web.id/2020/11/cara-mengganti-model-anime-live2d.html
